      <ul>
        <li>Most Viral, Most Innovative and Best Woman Razorpreneur get to win INR 1 lakh each</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="set rzp">
    <a href="#">
      What should I do if I encounter any issues while signing up or placing an order?
      <i class="fa-minus"></i>
    </a>
