  </div>
  <div class="set rzp">
    <a href="#">
      How can I track my order?
      <i class="fa-minus"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="content cust">
      You can track shipment of your order on the dashboard page by entering your login details.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="set rzp">
    <a href="#">
      How can I track my performance?
      <i class="fa-minus"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="content cust">
